      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is a mechanically sorted example featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant paired with a crisp G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The IMS bearing has been proactively addressed with a ceramic dual-row retrofit, and the rear main seal remains leak-free. Performance is bolstered by the factory M030 sport suspension and staggered 18-inch Carrera II alloys. The Variocam Plus system ensures a linear power delivery throughout the rev range, while the four-piston monobloc Brembo calipers provide consistent, fade-resistant deceleration. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the chassis dynamics and powertrain synchronization remain tight and responsive.",
